column4: hello everyone, does anyone know how to get nautilus 3.5.90 installed on quantal? I installed the beta an updated it, but nautilus is still on 3.4.2
quantal support in #ubuntu+1, and nautilus was reverted to 3.4 for quantal because there isn't time to adapt to all the changes in 3.5 before the release
is there a way to get 3.5.90 installed through a PPA?
take it to #ubuntu+1 and I'll check
